{"tid":1516844,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"圍狗屋係撚狗唔係比狗撚","createTime":"2019-08-29T16:55:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T07:59:32.000Z","uid":129622,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d6daf37b75237460974c18397077df2f6032c71b","tid":1516844,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:55:31.000Z","msg":"隔區食左幾晚糖水想講三樣野<br />\n<br />\n首先唔好比佢激親<br />\n唔好話「笑乜撚野」「講乜啊你」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">因為我地係唔需要比反應佢地</span><br />\n比狗所做既任何野挑動到自己 即係比人撚緊<br />\n人地講句曱甴就扯火？ 佢地聽到黑警 狗已經麻木哂<br />\n我地講既要更深入 更賤 更侮辱 <br />\n包括講到佢身邊既親友<br />\n可以講下佢個仔 <br />\n未有仔？會唔會小產啊？<br />\n未結婚？娶個警嫂比我屌啊<br />\n未有女朋友？遲一日溝女 條女就比人屌多日架喇<br />\n<br />\n然後請警覺性高D<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">班狗已經唔會係你面前集結 亦唔會坐狗車<br />\n而係幾條街外慢慢分散準備</span><br />\n好容易就包抄到<br />\n街坊人裝都唔夠 唔會打狗 <br />\n你要肯定自己有路走<br />\n睇唔到轉角位有冇人＝走唔到<br />\n<br />\n最後請唔好玩死一個位<br />\n前一晚就係到清場<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係啊有人話上一晚好醒走得到<br />\n問題係狗已經知道你地點走啊</span><br />\n但大家無諗過同一條路有狗包抄點算<br />\n擺幾隻狗你已經無得郁<br />\n如果班狗真係咁on9同一個位都比你走到幾晚 我地嬴撚左<br />\n事實上班狗有指揮有部處係唔會咁on9<br />\n我老母睇完google map唔洗五分鐘都諗到點包抄<br />\n<br />\n圍狗屋本身已經好危險<br />\n我地無大台 <br />\n屌緊狗又懶睇哨兵<br />\n有人話有狗要走又比人屌<br />\n知唔知自己安全先係最重要<br />\n衰左入去我地就少個手足 下次真係上戰場就少個幫手"},{"pid":"0baef7fcc3f4bb9d2556edc45c4c67bc4c5e7eec","tid":1516844,"uid":129622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:57:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyFriWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyFriWu.jpg&h=47e393ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e55f5fdbd72aafb0d61c7b1c5da3f0bd52cca40","tid":1516844,"uid":129622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:57:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/29/224714_f213ce2ab81d526cd21b2f2a7a29e6f3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F29%2F224714_f213ce2ab81d526cd21b2f2a7a29e6f3.png&h=ca2c8a50&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ed561e9ba3197ab2f0df322a1483aeb880f6856","tid":1516844,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:57:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/29/224658_dc298c5eb9517dfc4250e9711a305411.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F29%2F224658_dc298c5eb9517dfc4250e9711a305411.jpeg&h=3d153f59&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ec502e68b049fae5bad36dbb6f54f77f3e1eaa1","tid":1516844,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:58:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f7dd8be7d3cb5387c3cdb8cc5992f9c9b6595d8","tid":1516844,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:59:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y3TJbo3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy3TJbo3.jpg&h=fd249782&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd1942391517862704f241452efcbe07fb4cc9b3","tid":1516844,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wOJ86Xo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwOJ86Xo.jpg&h=adb0bf0d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe9240beb4f63f74f03c7becfcaedfb00d56fa1b","tid":1516844,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:00:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8629210948ddb9e9d161d493f4c4b1dbbc066c36","tid":1516844,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:00: